{
  "stem": "4122.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one-- this Roman Biletsky is a Jehovah's Witness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They took me there to the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I saw this group, so I didn't want to leave no more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was four-- four months still with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were hiding in a forest from pines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The pines are so low.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there, we had a bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were hiding there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the wintertime, when it was snowing, we couldn't go out for the-- for the wood, or water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We used to scrub the snow and dissolve it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the bunker where we were was a small place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was on one side higher, and the other side higher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like two beds made.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were 23 people, so 10 people were on this side, and 10 on this side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the middle was like a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The two pails-- it was a hole-- two holes-- and we had a pail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And behind this, we could make an oven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was like you could make a fire, and we cooked there at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Outside we had to see that the smoke shall not go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We used to stay there and watch, always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we were in there was a little place that three people could stand up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There wasn't place to turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When we were laying and sleeping, nobody could lay flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were all only on the side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[CRYING] When we wanted to turn, everybody had to turn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when we wanted to wash up, so one could wash one night, the other a night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it was such-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] such a hard life there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
